# Root .gitignore for Games repository
# Handles multiple Unity projects (SHIFT, SHIFT_Unity, etc.)

**/[Ll]ibrary/
**/[Tt]emp/
**/[Oo]bj/
**/[Bb]uild/
**/[Bb]uilds/
**/[Ll]ogs/
**/[Uu]ser[Ss]ettings/

# MemoryCaptures can get excessive in size.
**/[Mm]emoryCaptures/

# Recordings can get excessive in size
**/[Rr]ecordings/

# Autogenerated Jetbrains Rider plugin
**/[Aa]ssets/Plugins/Editor/JetBrains*

# Visual Studio cache directory
.vs/
**/.vs/

# Gradle cache directory
.gradle/
**/.gradle/

# Autogenerated VS/MD/Consulo solution and project files
**/ExportedObj/
**/.consulo/
*.csproj
*.unityproj
*.sln
*.suo
*.tmp
*.user
*.userprefs
*.pidb
*.booproj
*.svd
*.pdb
*.mdb
*.opendb
*.VC.db

# Unity3D generated meta files
*.pidb.meta
*.pdb.meta
*.mdb.meta

# Unity3D generated file on crash reports
**/sysinfo.txt

# Builds
*.apk
*.aab
*.unitypackage
*.app

# OS X trash and generated files
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Icon
._*

# Windows generated files
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
ehthumbs_vista.db
*.cab
*.lnk

# Sensitive Firebase config files
**/google-services.json
**/google-services.json.meta
**/GoogleService-Info.plist
**/GoogleService-Info.plist.meta

# Firebase generated Android repo
**/GeneratedLocalRepo/
**/GeneratedLocalRepo.meta

# Firebase large native binaries
**/Firebase/Plugins/x86_64/
**/Firebase/Plugins/x86/

# VS Code settings
.vscode/
**/.vscode/
